com.solidfire.element.api

Class Schedule

  • Object
    • Schedule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Schedule
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Schedule Schedule is an object containing information about each schedule created to autonomously make a snapshot of a volume. The return object includes information for all schedules. If scheduleID is used to identify a specific schedule then only information for that scheduleID is returned. Schedules information is returned with the API method, see ListSchedules on the SolidFire API guide page 245.
